OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,FWater companies could be fined up to a
OL,8,F10th of their turnover for poor
OL,9,Fcustomer service, under new powers
OL,10,Fgiven to the water regulator for
OL,11,FEngland and Wales.
OL,13,FOfwat said there are too many
OL,14,Finstances where customers feel let
OL,15,Fdown and their supplier does not have
OL,16,Ftheir best interests at heart.
