OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,FThe chief executive of the watchdog,
OL,8,FDavid Black, said: "From today we are
OL,9,Fputting water companies on notice to
OL,10,Fimprove customer service and where we
OL,11,Fsee failure, Ofwat can and will take
OL,12,Faction which could result in
OL,13,Fsignificant fines."
OL,15,FThe organisation has been introducing
OL,16,Fnew measures designed to protect
OL,17,Fconsumers and the environment.
