OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,FIt already has the power to block
OL,8,Fcompanies paying out money to
OL,9,Fshareholders if they fail to meet
OL,10,Fperformance standards, and can impose
OL,11,Ffines.
OL,13,FOfwat said it thinks being able to
OL,14,Fdish out penalties to suppliers not
OL,15,Ftreating customers fairly, triggered
OL,16,Fby a new licence requirement, will
OL,17,F"deliver real improvements in customer
OL,18,Fservice across the sector".
