OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,F"It is in the companies' interests to
OL,8,Fput customers at the heart of their
OL,9,Fbusiness and provide levels of service
OL,10,Fthat increase customer satisfaction,"
OL,11,FMr Black added.
OL,13,FThe watchdog's latest performance
OL,14,Freport showed there has been a fall in
OL,15,Fcustomer satisfaction across most of
OL,16,Fthe companies it regulates.
OL,18,FA separate report by the Consumer
OL,19,FCouncil for Water (CCW) in September
OL,20,Ffound that Southern Water was the most
OL,21,Fcomplained-about company.
