OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,FComplaints received by Southern Water
OL,8,Fwere almost three times higher than
OL,9,Fthe overall average for water and
OL,10,Fsewerage companies, while Thames
OL,11,FWater's were just over one-and-a-half
OL,12,Ftimes higher.
OL,14,FMore than 230,000 complaints were made
OL,15,Fto water companies in England and
OL,16,FWales by households in 2022 to 2023.
