OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,FMike Keil, chief executive of the CCW,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Every water company should
OL,9,Fprovide excellent customer service but
OL,10,Ftoo often through our research and the
OL,11,Fcomplaints we handle we see people
OL,12,Fbeing badly let down, particularly by
OL,13,Fpoor communication.
OL,15,F"A complete change in culture is
OL,16,Fneeded in some companies if we're to
OL,17,Fimprove people's experiences and
OL,18,Frepair fractured trust, and the new
OL,19,Fcustomer licence condition can help to
OL,20,Ffocus minds."
