OL,3,CWater firms face 'significant' fines
OL,4,Cfor poor customer service under new
OL,5,Cpowers
OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Barclay
OL,8,Fsaid: "We expect water companies to
OL,9,Fensure customers are properly
OL,10,Fsupported when services are disrupted.
OL,12,F"Enforcement action for poor customer
OL,13,Fservice is an important and necessary
OL,14,Fstep to restoring trust in the water
OL,15,Fsector and has been made possible
OL,16,Fthanks to government giving Ofwat
OL,17,Fincreased powers to modify the
OL,18,Flicences of companies in England under
OL,19,Fthe Environment Act.
